headline.print_headline: Poland, Ukraine Bar Overflight by Russian Defense Minister's Plane
headline.main: Poland, Ukraine Bar Overflight by Russian Defense Minister's Plane

lead_paragraph: Poland and Ukraine refused permission for a plane carrying Russian Defense Minister Sergei Shoigu to use their airspace on Friday while returning home from a visit to Slovakia.
